employ this ritual is 10\%.  It can affect any earth or stone within
10 feet (+ 10 / Rank) of the Adept.  It cannot be resisted.  Once cast,
it lasts for 1 hour (+ 1 / Rank) or until the Adept's concentration is
broken.
