resulting number is equal to or less than the Adept's Magical
Aptitude, then a number of small animals appear equal to the Adept's
Rank (1 if the Adept has no Rank with the ritual).  The animal the
Adept attempts to summon must be a native of the area.  If the Adept
chooses to vocalize his summons (assuming they are not attempting to
go undetected since the vocalization must be in the form of a shout or
call), the Base Chance is increased by 25.
